    • Method Detail

      • askForOverwrite

        boolean askForOverwrite(java.io.File toBeReplaced)
        Called to request user feedback. Implementations should display a question like "A file called 'toBeReplaced' already exists. Do you want to replace it?" to the user.
        Parameters:
        toBeReplaced - a file carrying the same name as the file currently to be renamed
        Returns:
        true if the file should be replaced, false otherwise
